Package com.ibm.jaggr.service.transport

Interface Summary
IHttpTransport Instances of IHttpTransport are responsible for parsing the HTTP request to extract request information such as module list, feature lists and other request parameters, and then 'decorating' the request with the processed values as defined types in request attributes.
IHttpTransportExtensionPoint  
 

Enum Summary
IHttpTransport.LayerContributionType Enum defining the constants for the various layer contribution types.
IHttpTransport.OptimizationLevel Supported optimization levels.
